y with iron grilles in buildings to MCD for action", "para": "Delhi High Court has directed the Municipal Corporation of Delhi (MCD) to consider a pending representation regarding hazardous cage-like iron grilles and illegal projections in residential buildings. The court deemed a Public Interest Litigation seeking their removal too broad.  The petitioner highlighted recent fire tragedies, like the Vivek Vihar incident, where blocked escape routes exacerbated loss of life, emphasizing the urgent need for safety improvements.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/delhi-high-court-directs-mcd-to-address-hazardous-iron-grilles-in-residential-buildings/132134043?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-137773/132134043.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}]}